    "description": "The SafeNet HighAssurance 4000 Gateway is a high performance, integrated security appliance that offers Gigabit Ethernet IPSEC encryption. Housed in a tamper evident chassis, the Security Gateway has two Gigabit Ethernet ports. Traffic on the local port is received in the clear, while traffic on the remote port has security processing applied to it. With the implementation of firmware version 2.2, the SafeNet HA 4000 can now be set-up and configured with the Safe Enterprise Security Management Center (SMC).",
